name: Kitsune Knight Lorraine
text:
Cannot be destroyed by battle with a monster that has the same ATK. If this card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent. If your opponent controls a Fiend-type monster, you can Normal Summon this card without Tributes, and if you do, this card gains 600 ATK.
